description.narrative: M&E's established tools and procedures in UNICEF Colombia, allowed Programme Coordination and Management, to formulate, monitor and report actions and achievements for all Annual Work Plans signed with the Colombian government, in a timely and effective manner. Overall, the Country Office continues to thrive for applying a Results-Based Management approach, that fosters objectivity in monitoring, transparency in reporting, programmatic learning and the generation of new, practical knowledge, for new, improved programming. These functions were carried out in coordination with all programmatic components, as well as with government allies, implementing partners and sister agencies of the United Nations System. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:06/02/2020
